{"tid":2281953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★病毒變種 研發中疫苗恐失效！！！","createTime":"2020-11-11T13:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T05:30:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1534025863a92c8008f2fafcda05d9f0a9824502","tid":2281953,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"近月丹麥逾二百個水貂養殖場爆發新型冠狀病毒疫情，不止水貂染疫，病毒更出現變異，再由水貂傳染給至少12人，逾250萬隻水貂被撲殺。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>當局擔心病毒變種令研發中的疫苗失效</strong></span>，上周下令緊急撲殺全國共1700萬隻水貂，但被質疑沒有科學和法律基礎。<br />\n<br />\n首相弗雷澤里克森周一承認有關決定不合法，叫停「格殺令」，並向國會提案立法，撲殺水貂及在2021年底前禁止養殖水貂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=412522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412522&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=db45a6a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412522&h=4c37eba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=412522</a>"},{"pid":"3695e0611f22602e10516be3f6d64da3f5a21c65","tid":2281953,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c174310631db1a7b854e7d2d6dda97c46424ebe0","tid":2281953,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjchpr2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsjchpr2.jpg&h=ad336d70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f06dc94fb